  "title": "Bows to Magic Staves CIT",
  "description": "Changes bows to magical staves. 12 unique models!",
  "body": "<p>Hello friends. This is a fun project I had the idea to start after working on a while back to see if it would be possible to transform bows into something else!<br />With this pack, you can transform a bow into any of the 12 staff models this pack provides by renaming it with an anvil.<br /><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">The pack requires OptiFine, which can be downloaded here: </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https://optifine.net/home\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://optifine.net/home</a> </span></p>\n<p><br /><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Here is the naming guide: </span><br /><span style=\"color: #3366ff;\"><a style=\"color: #3366ff;\" href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fnGYiRIi5coMSX1xiZG4sh8-lsjnPtS1ETLlbW2IK4M/edit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1fnGYiRIi5coMSX1xiZG4sh8-lsjnPtS1ETLlbW2IK4M/edit</a></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/fEVLPy/2018_07_03_23_00_49.png\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/XDcNrZz/gif.gif\" width=\"1166\" height=\"657\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/g60gjYP/screenshots-compiled.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tDTGrJS/staves-compiled.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://image.ibb.co/ihPxhJ/2018_07_03_20_19_15.png\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Staff names:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Night Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Staff of Unholy Wisdom</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Bermunde Hermit Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Northgate Guardian Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Golden Crook</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Holy Celtic Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Goblin Witch Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Sagrada Winged Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Divine Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Olwen Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Lich Staff</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Black Snake Staff</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
